Gallery Mein Real Photos Kaise Lagayein (Future)
Jab bhi photos add karni ho:
Step 1 — Photo ko repo mein upload karo (same jagah jahan index.html hai)
Step 2 — Gallery section mein yeh wala part dhundo:

html<div class="gallery-item">
  <div class="gallery-placeholder">📷</div>
  <div class="gallery-overlay" id="t-g1">Wedding</div>
</div>

Badlo is se:

html<div class="gallery-item">
  <img src="wedding1.jpg" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover"/>
  <div class="gallery-overlay" id="t-g1">Wedding</div>
</div>
Step 3 — 6 boxes hain gallery mein, sabko isi tarah replace karo apni photos se.

Photo Names simple rakho jaise:
wedding1.jpg, bride1.jpg, drone1.jpg — spaces mat rakho naam mein, underscores ya numbers use karo. ✅
